Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm really going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?\NHurry it up, would you--
