Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Can we at least\Nhave a styptic pencil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? What do we do? She's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. Damn! Damn! This is disastrous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this, you idiot, Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You team up with Hana-{\i1}dono{\i0},\Nso that she only helps you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you go and injure me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, Gakuto, what are you talking--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}, explain yourself!\NWhat happened between you and Hana-{\i1}dono{\i0}?!
