Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you will.\NI can't stand that icky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm still out--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to have a word with you,\Nso come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair! You really are trying\Nto save just Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
