Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers. I'm going to\Nmake this the most terrifying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,most embarrassing night of your entire life!
