Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do what I can now.\NKiyoshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and the others are in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're making their move, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For the president's sake, I will\Ncompletely stamp out their scheme!
