Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "huh" me! Hurry up and pee\Nin there! We have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! Those scissors\Nweren't for snipping off my eryngii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I even trimmed off the spout to make\Nsure you didn't spill any, so get to it!
