Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get to that back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get that door unlocked, the\Nfirst stage of the mission will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, please hold it, and I will pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to hold it?!\NYou can hold it yourself, can't you?!
