Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't, it will go all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What is the deal\Nwith this idiot Kiyoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He pulls out his penis,\Nthen starts acting high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't back down, Hana! I'm a girl\Nwho gives as good as she gets! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be outdone by this guy!
