Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That will teach you, you idiot, Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so full of yourself,\Njust because your penis is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why did you take\Nyour panties off, Hana-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
