Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, I'm in total control here.\NNow, bask in the embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I don't know what's going on\Nanymore, but I can say one thing for certain--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I never dreamed I'd ever be\Nin this situation in my lifetime!
